GM Lucky Dood Holder,

It is with great pleasure that we inform you that you are forever a part of Bitcoin Blockchain history. You can find proof of this Dood's permanent inscription on the Bitcoin Blockchain [by clicking here](https://ordinals.com/content/21aa94f671d6e8d1dd9a23a77b6a0a2c355ecf08e536f6e4ece25a6a9c0928bei0?lighting_mode=dark&token_id=1).

We're also happy to tell you that:

> - This Dood was produced with love and care.

> - He was dripped out in the finest Ordinals swag.

> - He was dipped three times in the rainbow river, making him extra lucky.

Make sure to take your Dood with you everywhere you go. You never know when you need a little luck on your side.

Wishing you all the luck in the Metaverse,

Sincerely, from now till the end of time,

THE
